{
  "name": "react-native-latex-text",
  "version": "1.0.3",
  "description": "React Native/Expo LaTeX Formula Rendering Component, supports mixed typesetting of text and formulas, custom formula delimiters, automatic calculation of formula line height, based on MathJax SVG, built-in caching, no native dependencies. | React Native/Expo Latex 公式渲染组件，支持文字与公式混排/自定义公式分隔符，自动计算公式行高，基于 MathJax SVG，内置缓存，无原生依赖。",
  "main": "./lib/src/index.js",
  "types": "./lib/src/index.d.ts",
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "import": "./lib/src/index.js",
      "require": "./lib/src/index.js",
      "types": "./lib/src/index.d.ts"
    },
    "./tex-svg": {
      "import": "./lib/tex-svg.js",
      "require": "./lib/tex-svg.js",
      "types": "./lib/tex-svg.d.ts"
    }
  },
  "scripts": {
    "build": "tsc",
    "prepare": "npm run build",
    "prepublishOnly": "npm run build && npm test",
    "test": "echo \"No tests specified yet\" && exit 0"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "react-native",
    "expo",
    "mathjax",
    "latex",
    "formula",
    "svg",
    "math",
    "mathematics",
    "renderer"
  ],
  "author": "hutao_zyf",
  "license": "MIT",
  "peerDependencies": {
    "react": ">=16.8.0",
    "react-native": ">=0.60.0",
    "react-native-svg": ">=12.0.0",
    "react-native-webview": ">=11.0.0"
  },
  "peerDependenciesMeta": {
    "react-native-webview": {
      "optional": false
    },
    "react-native-svg": {
      "optional": false
    }
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/zyf2007/react-native-latex-text.git"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@types/react": "^19.2.14",
    "@types/react-native": ">=0.60.0",
    "react-native-svg": ">=12.0.0",
    "react-native-webview": ">=11.0.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "typescript": "^5.0.0",
    "@types/react-native": "^0.72.0"
  },
  "files": [
    "lib/",
    "README.md",
    "LICENSE"
  ],
  "publishConfig": {
    "access": "public"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=14.0.0",
    "npm": ">=6.0.0"
  }
}